project_descr: Strengthening Arab Economic Integration for Sustainable Development

outputs.output_descr: To provide support to League of Arab States (LAS) and its member states for PAFTA Upgrading as well as preparation process for the Arab Customs Union. Enhancement of economic partnership in the region through better Arab connectivity.

outputs.output_title: Trade and SDGs in Arab Region
outputs.output_descr: This project is proposed with the main objective of “Enhancing the working and policy level debate on trade that would be guided by the SDGs”.
